596
00:47:56,640 --> 00:47:57,473
(GRUNTS)

597
00:48:13,523 --> 00:48:15,358
Where is your boy,
Orange Juice?

598
00:48:25,769 --> 00:48:29,906
Don't worry,
I bet mother and father
