(HYENA CACKLING)

610
00:49:59,096 --> 00:50:00,396
(ZEBRA WHINES)

611
00:50:00,398 --> 00:50:02,264
No!

612
00:50:02,266 --> 00:50:06,769
Stop it! No!
Stop it! Stop it!

613
00:50:07,671 --> 00:50:09,071
