Yes! Yes!

626
00:52:27,544 --> 00:52:28,978
(SNARLING)

627
00:52:28,980 --> 00:52:30,613
No! No!

628
00:52:31,848 --> 00:52:33,482
No! No!

629
00:52:36,653 --> 00:52:37,953
(GRUNTS)

